  "ShortDescription": "Class 3 Casemate Coilgun",
  "LongDescription": "Despite its high-tech sound, this plasma cannon is actually a relatively crude solution to the Protectorate's problem of being out-armored in every weight class.  These coilguns fire a magnetic bottle containing superheated plasma which shatters against the armor of a warship and melts large holes, opening it up for attack from lighter caliber weaponry such as 100mm.",
  "FlavorText": "TO: NOVANCE\nFROM: PROTECTORATE NAVAL COMMAND\nCLASSIFIED\n\nI'm transferring the Otdel's briefing on the Jinn to you, Vance, but I suspect you'll have no problem getting your crews familiar with its operation and finding creative ways to use it on your lineships. Cass has received personal authorization for her skunkworks to develop a sturdier option that should allow it to be utilized by more vessels without requiring additional materiel, but I understand that it may wind up being a fixed weapon in that case.\n\nRegardless, I have to remind you that this is a dangerous device and I advise against fueling your habit of overcharging it. Play this one safe and textbook, I will not have any of our precious fleets vaporized by gung-ho captains attempting to one-up each other.",
